summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 65E, Page 158 of The Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Section 21, Township 24N, Range 4 East, W.M., extending 115' South of S. Angeline St. between Empire Way S. and 32nd Ave. S. from RD 5000 to RM 800. (C.F. 287782, Petition of James L. Halfon).
